title: [Kodachii's Weaponry]
description: Beneath an oak beam ceiling, a colorful Icemule map hangs on one of the smooth white plaster walls.  A large brass-bound chest and a long varnished counter sit in opposite corners while a knotted woolen rug rests on a russet oak floor.

Smooth white plaster walls rise from a russet oak floor.  Just above a knotted woolen rug hangs a colorful Icemule map, and an oak beam ceiling completes the picture.  A long varnished counter and a large brass-bound chest stand side by side in the middle of the room.
